Add, memo[i]+memo[i-1] element and keep updating the memory array in each pass of N.

**When n=3**
i=1,  memo[1] = memo[1] +memo[0] = 1+1 = 2
i=2,  memo[2] = memo[2] +memo[1] = 1+2 = 3
i=3,  memo[3] = memo[3] +memo[2] = 1+3 = 4
i=4,  memo[4] = memo[4] +memo[3] = 1+4 = 5
New Memory Array : [1,2,3,4,5]

**When n=2**
i=1,  memo[1] = memo[1] +memo[0] = 2+1 = 3
i=2,  memo[2] = memo[2] +memo[1] = 3+3 = 6
i=3,  memo[3] = memo[3] +memo[2] = 4+6 = 10
i=4,  memo[4] = memo[4] +memo[3] = 5+10 = 15
New Memory Array : [1,3,6,10,15]

