# Intuition
Rule 1: two negatives turn to two positives 
Rule 2: one positive and one negative can swap the sign with each other 
Summarize: ultimately, we can group all negative signs together by using rule 2 and turn all of them into one negative with rule 1, so if there are odd negative signs, only one will be left, otherwisde all of them will turn to positive signs 

